===Pro Bowlers===
The [[Pro Bowl]] is the annual [[all-star game]] of the NFL. Pro Bowl rosters are determined by a combination of fan, player, and coach voting.<ref name="Peyton Manning tops Tom Brady in fans' Pro Bowl voting">{{cite web|url=http://www.nfl.com/probowl/story/0ap1000000114155/article/peyton-manning-tops-tom-brady-in-fans-pro-bowl-voting|title=Peyton Manning tops Tom Brady in fans' Pro Bowl voting|date=December 20, 2012|publisher=NFL.com|accessdate=April 28, 2013}}</ref>

